{"tid":1358442,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"唔好入村！唔好搞祠堂！","createTime":"2019-07-24T02:32:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-24T02:53:46.000Z","uid":242792,"like":12,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"8fdd09ff895ca8de4a2478d2e8bce9dd26ddf5cd","tid":1358442,"uid":242792,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T02:32:21.000Z","msg":"唔好入村！<br />\n唔好搞祠堂！<br />\n唔好搞祠堂！<br />\n唔好搞祠堂！<br />\n好多祠堂係古蹟嚟！<br />\n請針對返政權！<br />\n而唔係人民鬥人民，政府坐漁人之利！<br />\n五大訴求！義士遺願大家係咪唔記得呀？！<br />\n遊行係話俾官警黑知，我哋唔怕，唔怕恐襲！<br />\n但唔代表要專登搞人。<br />\n圍元朗警署我可以理解，因為佢哋要交代。<br />\n河妖山墳俾人搞，黑鬥黑我食花生，<br />\n但遊行一定唔入得村，唔可以搞祠堂！<br />\n唔係以後「和理非」點做盾？"},{"pid":"65af463de0e8f76f59d267aca31fb72f9e0f9899","tid":1358442,"uid":165246,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T02:34:44.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><br />\n唔好比五毛分化<br />\n<br />\n請大家一定要記得！！！！<br />\n１。全面撤回逃犯條例<br />\n２。撤銷暴動定性<br />\n３。釋放被捕義士並承諾永不追究<br />\n４。全面實行雙普選<br />\n５。成立獨立調查委員會追究黑警責任＋徹查警黑勾結元朗站暴打站內市民<br />\n6 。721上環對示威者開36槍 義士被狗開槍擊中<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n光復香港 時代革命<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},{"pid":"29411db9e343304c00eacc57c9ab7ec9aae26c42","tid":1358442,"uid":242792,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T02:45:29.000Z","msg":"你真係想報仇，有好多方法。<br />\n唔洗用拳頭。<br />\n你咪喪report佢哋潛建囉。<br />\n佢哋實有做生意，起底罷食罷買！<br />\n搞祠堂係幫政府送子彈！"},{"pid":"873d355bee249a6d71644401779533316a940e1d","tid":1358442,"uid":220864,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T02:46:10.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">大家小心<br />\n開始有三毛想搧動義士搞無差別攻擊<br />\n<br />\n到時真係搞到同班白衫佬打立場姐姐打大肚婆一樣<br />\n班友係想幫政府繼續激化民鬥民策略<br />\n記住，獨立思考<br />\n唔好俾人帶風向</span>"},{"pid":"676d39c8e775acebdfd9b80eb3841cd86213c10a","tid":1358442,"uid":28558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T02:47:14.000Z","msg":"P<br />\n完全封鎖<br />\n上一頁"},{"pid":"6134c0ea17537a38c48f68bd667dd9e0e8006dbd","tid":1358442,"uid":122676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T02:47:26.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9f8360eba3d3bad800281591b07b34fb4fcfbb00","tid":1358442,"uid":242792,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"676d39c8e775acebdfd9b80eb3841cd86213c10a","tid":1358442,"uid":28558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T02:47:14.000Z","msg":"P<br />\n完全封鎖<br />\n上一頁"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T02:53:46.000Z","msg":"淨係識睇p就鎖，用下腦啦"}]}